  "description": "A nighttime panoramic view of a city skyline illuminated with city lights and a firework display. In the foreground is a modern bridge with bright white lights stretching across dark water. Behind the bridge is a classic suspension bridge. The city skyline is densely packed with buildings, some reaching towards the sky with illuminated spires. Above the skyline is a burst of fireworks, appearing as a bright, white, and slightly blurred cloud. The overall scene conveys a sense of celebration and urban grandeur.",
